Comments
Dynatrace automates backup failure detection, ServiceNow incident creation/update, and email reporting. PowerShell provides supporting on-demand validation for workload-specific checks between Dynatrace cycles. Failure remediation, owner communication, investigation notes, and incident closure remain manual to ensure proper operational review before action or closure.
